# Local Plugin Execution

- OaC work runs locally in WSL in `~/OaC`.
- Do not use Omnistation as an execution workspace for OaC.
- Remote hosts may be used for non-critical research only.
- Plugin and connector plans are documented under `docs/plugin-plans/`.
- Plans must distinguish:
  - proposed intent,
  - plan preview,
  - human review,
  - reconciler execution,
  - audit evidence,
  - Day2 drift handling.
- No secrets, API keys, browser callback tokens, or local credentials may be stored in the repository.
